.0 · 引擎存取 Port 抽象需求\\n\\n> **状态：** 已定稿，供实现与 Review / gbx 引用。  \\n> **性质：** 将引擎与具体存储 IO **程序拆清 + 物理拆清**：引擎只暴露存/取协议（callback / Port）；现网 JSON+fs+SQLite 实现迁出到 Studio V2 `engineIOModule`。  \\n> **协议真源（工程）：** [技术设计 23-引擎存取Port与IO适配](../../技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。  \\n> **用法入口：** [packages/rpg-engine/README.md](../../../../packages/rpg-engine/README.md)。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. 本轮定位\\n\\n### 1.1 要做什么\\n\\n```text\\n程序边界\\n  · 引擎纯逻辑：不直接依赖 node:fs / better-sqlite3 实现\\n  · 引擎暴露存/取 Port（callback）+ 固定请求/响应协议\\n  · 宿主注入 Port；引擎只调 Port，不关心介质\\n\\n物理边界\\n  · 现网 IO 实现从 packages/rpg-engine 迁出\\n  · 落入 apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/（本机 Studio 默认适配）\\n  · Next / Host 装配处创建并注入\\n\\n文档\\n  · 技术设计 23 为协议定稿；18/19/20 过期表述 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-b0a736b9-3898-44e6-a7c0-0b3892a0781b-7\\nfc_bf666ea2-0b98-9205-946a-321b4ff37446_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports/STATE.json\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"{\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"BATCH_REVIEW\\\",\\n  \\\"currentBatch\\\": 2,\\n  \\\"batchFixAttempts\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"fullFixAttempts\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"checkboxFixAttempts\\\": 0,\\n  \\\"iteration\\\": 7,\\n  \\\"lastSuccessfulCommit\\\": null,\\n  \\\"manualQaRequired\\\": false,\\n  \\\"blockedReason\\\": null,\\n  \\\"activeTaskIds\\\": [\\n    \\\"V2-IO-3\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"exFile\\\": \\\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_执行索引.md\\\",\\n  \\\"fixTrigger\\\": null,\\n  \\\"lastVerifyOk\\\": true,\\n  \\\"lastVerifySummary\\\": \\\"verify ok\\\",\\n  \\\"lastVerifyFingerprint\\\": null,\\n  \\\"lastVerifyReportPath\\\": \\\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports/reports/latest-verify.json\\\",\\n  \\\"ineffectiveFixStreak\\\": 0,\\n  [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":96,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-11\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_0\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/README.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# engineIOModule · 本机引擎存取 IO\\n\\n> **Server 区专用。** 禁止 `pageComponents` / `bis` / `stores` / `commonUiComponents` / `ajaxProxy` / `typeFiles` 及任何 `\\\"use client\\\"` 模块引用本目录。  \\n> 协议真源：[技术设计 23](../../../docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/23-引擎存取Port与IO适配.md)。  \\n> 需求：[引擎存取Port抽象_需求.md](../../../docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/引擎存取Port抽象_需求.md)。\\n\\n## 职责\\n\\n本目录承载 **Studio V2 本机** 对引擎 Port 的 IO 实现（JSON+fs / SQLite / jsonl）。  \\n引擎只声明 Port；**不** import 本模块。装配发生在 Next API / Host 单例处：`createEngineIOPorts(dataRoot)` → `createEngineHost({ ...ports })`。\\n\\n## 目录\\n\\n```text\\nengineIOModule/\\n  content/                 # ContentPort：Workspace / 包 / 角色 / 资产 meta 读（V2-IO-6）\\n  profile/                 # ProfilePort：薄 Profile 读写（V2-IO-5）\\n [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":97,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-12\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/createEngineIOPorts.ts\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"/**\\n\\t* 模块名称：本机引擎 IO 装配工厂（骨架）\\n\\t* 模块说明：按 dataRoot 创建 Memory / Profile / Content / EngineLog Ports。\\n\\t* Server 边界：仅 app/api、Host 装配、*.server.ts、utils/server 可引用；\\n\\t* 禁止 Client（pageComponents / bis / stores / typeFiles / ajaxProxy 等）任何 import。\\n\\t* 实现迁入节奏见里程碑 V2-IO-4～V2-IO-7；本文件在 V2-IO-3 仅占位，避免误用未迁完的装配。\\n\\t*/\\nimport type {\\n\\tContentPort,\\n\\tEngineLogPort,\\n\\tMemoryPort,\\n\\tProfilePort,\\n} from \\\"@airpc/rpg-engine\\\";\\n\\n/** 本机 Studio 注入 Host 的四 Port 套件（技术设计 23）。 */\\nexport type EngineIOPorts = {\\n\\tmemory: MemoryPort;\\n\\tprofile: ProfilePort;\\n\\tcontent: ContentPort;\\n\\tengineLog: EngineLogPort;\\n};\\n\\n/**\\n\\t* 创建指向 `dataRoot` 的本机 Ports。\\n\\t* V2-IO-3 骨架阶段尚未迁入实现；调用方须等 V2-IO-4+ 完 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":111,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-19\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_8\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/profile/README.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# profile/\\n\\n**ProfilePort** 本机实现落点（`data/users/<userId>/profile.save.json` 读写）。\\n\\n- 刀序：V2-IO-5\\n- **Server 区**：禁止 Client 引用\\n\",\"isEmpty\":false,\"exceededLimit\":false,\"totalLines\":7,\"fileSize\":162,\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/profile/README.md\",\"readRange\":{\"startLine\":1,\"endLine\":7},\"relatedCursorRulePaths\":[],\"relatedCursorRules\":[]}}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-bbb0764a-3e38-48f4-b361-21a9e2664f4b-19\\nfc_25bcc58b-af09-9c37-be70-af5125106c31_8\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784781458414\",\"completedAtMs\":\"1784781458566\"},\"model_call_id\":\"2310601a-1e8e-4d84-91ad-c4a6d394ccba-3-b797\",\"session_id\":\"d63bd641-12cd-4e19-ad56-02438074c485\" [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":174,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-7f8a24b0-19ae-4dc4-bd35-fe88751d5fd0-22\\nfc_f051eb83-c056-9739-8a59-64c08fdf4c58_1\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"verify NOT run|Shell denied|quality:studio|V2-IO-3|✅|DONE|summary|createEngineIOPorts\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-engine-io-ports/prompts/agent-178478